column15:
The distortion tactic is used in the following post: 

@JLMelenchon S'il n'y avait pas l'OTAN nous serions tous morts ou tous russes !! 

This post distorts the main message of the topic by oversimplifying the potential consequences of the NATO's involvement in global affairs. It presents a false dichotomy and misrepresents the complex role and impact of NATO in international relations.
